1. Dependencies

	First satisfy dependencies from original INSTALL

	- Mojolicious (https://metacpan.org/release/Mojolicious)
	- Data::Printer (https://metacpan.org/release/Data-Printer)
	- Mojolicious::Plugin::ConfigHashMerge (https://metacpan.org/release/Mojolicious-Plugin-ConfigHashMerge)
	- Mojolicious::Plugin::Database (https://metacpan.org/release/Mojolicious-Plugin-Database)

2. Setup Web server

	Example for nginx 1.12.1 to use the mojo app as replacement:

	location ~ ^/cgi-bin/tipp.cgi$ {
		auth_basic      "TIPP";
		auth_basic_user_file    /some/path/htpasswd.users;
		rewrite /(.*) /api  break;
		proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3000;
	}
